In the following, we compare our result with recent studies on strong coupling of single emitters using plasmonic nanocavities. To date, most strong coupling studies have relied on multiple (
  n) emitters in the form of J-aggregates (
  
   43
  ) to induce a large collective effect (








      g
      ‚àù




